@startuml
title Capture Sequence with Common Environment Profile

actor Operator
participant "tools/exp" as Tool
participant "csi_capture.cli" as CLI
participant "core.environment" as Env
participant "core.device" as Dev
participant "capture.py" as Capture
participant "ESP32 RX Serial" as Serial
database "manifest.json + capture files" as Store

Operator -> Tool : capture --experiment ... --target-profile esp32s3_csi_v1
Tool -> CLI : invoke args
CLI -> Env : resolve_environment_profile(profile_id)
Env --> CLI : EnvironmentProfile
CLI -> Dev : resolve_serial_device(...)
Dev --> CLI : device path + realpath
CLI -> Dev : validate_serial_device_access(path)
Dev --> CLI : access OK
CLI -> Capture : serial_lines(port, baud)\ncapture_stream(...)
Capture -> Serial : read CSI_DATA lines
Serial --> Capture : raw serial stream
Capture --> CLI : parsed packet rows
CLI -> Store : write frames + metadata OR run manifests
CLI --> Operator : summary + records count

@enduml
